# Coinc
Coinc is an Alfred workflow which do currency conversion by using live currency rates from Open Exchange Rates API.
![Demo Screenshot](images/demo.png)
For list of support currencies, Installation, Setup and Usage, see [Wiki](https://github.com/tomy0000000/Coinc/wiki)
Credentials to acquire currency rates. Can be obtained by signing up a free, deletable account
For number formatting (e.g. decimal separator). Find one in this ICU list, normally looks like {language}_{COUNTRY}
